; Coverage for report.cc: posts_report with --group-by and --limit combined
; Exercises the group_by_ branch in posts_report (lines 349-353) with a
; limit predicate to filter postings before grouping.

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 Restaurant
    Expenses:Dining    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $40.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --group-by payee --limit 'amount > 0'
Grocery Store
24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
24-Feb-15 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $40.00       $90.00

Restaurant
24-Jan-01 Restaurant            Expenses:Dining              $30.00       $30.00
end test
